'''Seer''' was a rank of the [[Priest caste]] of the [[Yuuzhan Vong]]. A seer was one who took the auguries of the [[Yun'o|Gods]], interpreted signs, and pronounced when the Yuuzhan Vong would be ready for a battle. Seers were often female and were often covered in black Yuuzhan Vong blood.<ref name="TUF">''[[The New Jedi Order: The Unifying Force]]''</ref>

There were variations upon the position of seer among the ranks of the Yuuzhan Vong. One such variation was that of the [[warrior-seer]], who provided both religious and tactical advice to senior Yuuzhan Vong [[Commander/Legends|commanders]]. A quartet of [[Royal Seers]] also accompanied [[Shimrra Jamaane]], the [[Supreme Overlord]] of the [[Yuuzhan Vong]], during the final days of the [[Yuuzhan Vong War]].<ref name="TUF" />

